                  <p>Being the THIRD SESSION in the Mayoralty of The Right Hon. 
                  <persName id="t17850223-12-person282">
                     RICHARD
                      CLARK
                  <interp inst="t17850223-12-person282" type="surname" value="CLARK"></interp>
