               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t17850223-12-punish65" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17850223-12-punish65" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850223-12-defend270 t17850223-12-punish65"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
